on promissory notes securities investments such as public local and corporate bonds as well as equity and other securities domestic and foreign exchange services and bonds and registration consignment services in addition it provides liabilities guarantee securities lending public bonds underwriting agency custody and financial instruments intermediary services overthecounter sale of public bonds trust services for secured corporate bonds interest rate currency and other derivative transaction services and overthecounter sale of insurance products further the company offers financial products and asset management consulting as well as corporate and specialty finance services aozora bank ltd serves retail customers large and midsized corporations public corporations and financial institutional customers as of march   it operated  domestic branches and  overseas representative offices the company was formerly known as nippon fudosan bank limited and changed its name to aozora bank ltd in  aozora bank ltd was founded in  and is headquartered in tokyo japan detailed description  kudanminami chomechiyodakutokyo  japanfounded in  employees phone     wwwaozorabankcojp key executives for aozora bank ltd aozora bank ltd does not have any key executives recorded aozora bank ltd key developments aozora bank ltd presents at infrastructure investors forum asia  jul jul   aozora bank ltd presents at infrastructure investors forum asia  jul  venue the westin singapore singapore aozora bank ltd board meeting jun   jul   aozora bank ltd board meeting jun   agenda to consider issuance of equity type stock options aozora bank ltd proposes amendments to its articles of incorporation may   aozora bank ltd at its agm to be held on june   proposed amendments to its articles of incorporation similar private companies by industry company name region abashiri shinkin bank asia aichi shinkin bank asia aichiken chuo shinyo kumiai asia aichiken iryo credit cooperative asia alps chuo shinkin ban