high levels of data quality and these characteristics guarantee a unique reportscope• examines and identifies key information and issues about aozora bank ltd for business intelligence requirements• studies and presents the companys strengths weaknesses opportunities growth potential and threats competition strategic and operational business information is objectively reported• provides data on company financial performance and competitive benchmarking• the profile also contains information on business operations company history major products and services key employees and locations and subsidiariesreasons to buy• quickly enhance your understanding of aozora bank ltd• gain insight into the marketplace and a better understanding of internal and external factors which could impact the industry• increase businesssales activities by understanding your competitors’ businesses better• recognize potential partnerships and supplierskey highlightsaozora bank ltd aozora is a commercial bank based in japan it offers a range of financial products and services in the areas of retail banking corporate banking business banking and financial markets the banks portfolio of offerings includes debit cards checking accounts savings accounts wealth management services and investment banking products it also provides lending securitization business and asset revitalization asset management loan syndication and investment advisory services in addition aozora also focuses on lending of securities underwriting of public bonds guarantee of liabilities trust business agency business overthecounter sales and financial instruments intermediary business the bank distributes its products and services to private individuals corporate entities and institutional clients in japan hong kong cayman islands the uk ireland and the us aozora is headquartered in tokyo japan table of contents aozora bank ltd  business analysis aozora bank ltd  company overview aozora bank ltd  business description aozora b