ummer of  with an eye toward an eventual merger banks had been hit by losses in the us subprime market the talks collapsed in may  amid disputes over capitalization and business strategy as well as the abatement of the  financial crisis aozora acquired japan wealth management securities in  merging it with existing subsidiary aozora securities in  in january  cerberus announced that it would sell most of its stake in aozora cutting its total share from  percent to  percent cerberus sold this last portion of its stake to barclays for distribution to other investors in august  ending cerberuss shareholding in aozora locationsedit aozora headquarters in tokyo aozoras head office is located in the kudan area of chiyoda city tokyo near yasukuni shrine the bank has retail branches in chiba fukuoka hiroshima kanazawa kyoto nagoya osaka namba and umeda sapporo sendai takamatsu tokyo ikebukuro jiyugaoka nihonbashi shibuya shinjuku and ueno and yokohama aozora also has representative offices in new york singapore seoul jakarta and shanghai and financing subsidiaries in the cayman islands hong kong luxembourg the united kingdom and the united states see alsoedit list of investors in bernard l madoff securities list of banks list of banks in japan referencesedit  corporate history retrieved on june    a b company profile retrieved on june    directors and auditors retrieved on february    corporate brochure  page three archived september   at the wayback machine retrieved on july    corporate brochure  page six archived september   at the wayback machine retrieved on july    a b c softbank makes deal for nippon credit  japan bank stake sale  statement on aozora’s exposure to madoff securities archived january   at the wayback machine retrieved on december    shinsei bank aozora bank launch merger talksnikkeipermanent dead link shinsei aozora banks in talks retrieved on may    shinsei aozora scrap merger government vows more oversight  httpwwwaozorabankcojpenglishaboutcorporateo